    <title>NewHexoBlog</title>
    <link href="http://yoursite.com/2017/04/29/NewHexoBlog/"/>
    <id>http://yoursite.com/2017/04/29/NewHexoBlog/</id>
    <published>2017-04-29T13:35:15.000Z</published>
    <updated>2017-04-29T13:58:19.894Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="Create-Hexo-Blog-step-by-step"><a href="#Create-Hexo-Blog-step-by-step" class="headerlink" title="Create Hexo Blog step by step"></a>Create Hexo Blog step by step</h2><h3 id="Step-1-install-git-nodejs"><a href="#Step-1-install-git-nodejs" class="headerlink" title="Step 1 install git,nodejs"></a>Step 1 install git,nodejs</h3><p><a href="https://git-scm.com/downloads" target="_blank" rel="external">Git</a><br><a href="https://nodejs.org/en/download/" target="_blank" rel="external">NodeJS</a></p>
<h3 id="Step-2-install-hexo"><a href="#Step-2-install-hexo" class="headerlink" title="Step 2 install hexo"></a>Step 2 install hexo</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ npm install -g hexo</div><div class="line">$ npm install</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="Step-3-create-folder-and-initilize"><a href="#Step-3-create-folder-and-initilize" class="headerlink" title="Step 3 create folder and initilize"></a>Step 3 create folder and initilize</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ <span class="built_in">cd</span> d:\GitHub</div><div class="line">$ mkdir hexo-blog</div><div class="line">$ hexo init</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="Step-4-generate-html-pages"><a href="#Step-4-generate-html-pages" class="headerlink" title="Step 4 generate html pages"></a>Step 4 generate html pages</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ hexo generate (hexo g)</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="Step-5-testing-in-local"><a href="#Step-5-testing-in-local" class="headerlink" title="Step 5 testing in local"></a>Step 5 testing in local</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ hexo server (hexo s)</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="Step-6-deploy-into-github"><a href="#Step-6-deploy-into-github" class="headerlink" title="Step 6 deploy into github"></a>Step 6 deploy into github</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>modify _config.yml, go to the end and add following lines:<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">deploy:</div><div class="line">  <span class="built_in">type</span>: git</div><div class="line">  repo: https://github.com/nateliu/nateliu.github.io.git</div><div class="line">  branch: master</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<h3 id="Step-7-launch-with-following-lines"><a href="#Step-7-launch-with-following-lines" class="headerlink" title="Step 7 launch with following lines"></a>Step 7 launch with following lines</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ hexo clean</div><div class="line">$ hexo generate</div><div class="line">$ hexo deploy</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="Step-8-go-to-chrome-to-see-the-result"><a href="#Step-8-go-to-chrome-to-see-the-result" class="headerlink" title="Step 8 go to chrome to see the result."></a>Step 8 go to chrome to see the result.</h3><p>My Hexo Blog: <a href="https://nateliu.github.io" target="_blank" rel="external">My-Hexo-Blog</a></p>
<h3 id="Step-9-my-source-for-hexo-blog"><a href="#Step-9-my-source-for-hexo-blog" class="headerlink" title="Step 9 my source for hexo-blog"></a>Step 9 my source for hexo-blog</h3><p><a href="https://github.com/nateliu/hexo-blog" target="_blank" rel="external">hexo-blog</a></p>
]]></content>
    
